    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "TO : Director, FBI",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "DATE: 4-3-52",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, Memphis (62-0)",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "SUBJECT: UNKNOWN SUBJECT; Flying Objects,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Nashville, Tennessee",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "INFORMATION CONCERNING",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Lt. Commander [REDACTED] U. S. Navy, temporarily residing",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "at [REDACTED] Nashville, Tennessee, advised SAA [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "of the Nashville Resident Agency on March 14, 1952, at approximately 2:15 p.m.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "of the following incident.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] stated that approximately 10:20 p.m. on March 13, 1952,",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "while standing in the back yard of 1900 Graybar Lane and looking toward",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "the moon, which was then in the southwest section of the sky, he observed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "an object which appeared approximately 20 degrees above the horizon.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "Lt. [REDACTED] described this object as being circular in shape, approximately",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "one-half the size of the moon, deep bright blue in color, very vivid blue.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "He stated the object had a slight reddish fringe on the aft end. The",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "object appeared to be moving from the northwest to the southeast. He",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "stated that the object was not in his vision more than three seconds.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "It made no sound. Lt. [REDACTED] stated that at the time he observed this,",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "there were no clouds in the sky, the stars were out, and the moon was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "full. Lt. [REDACTED] stated that the only way he could describe it was that",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "it appeared to be a very high powered spotlight on a cloud, but he did",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "not believe this could have been the cause of that which he had seen",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "because he had not seen any spotlight or any strong search lights there",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "during the evening.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "The above is being furnished for your information, and no action is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "contemplated by this office unless advised to the contrary.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
